liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Root was trying to get to his fifty in one blow and went barrelling down the deck, trying to heave Nathan Lyon over cow corner, but the ball dipped and spun through the gate and Alex Carey completed a superb stumping. Lyon was coming around the wicket, so Carey's view of the ball would've been obscured for most of its journey. Great play from Carey. Jonny Bairstow could never. Missed opportunity for Joe Root, but the half-century was never the point of this innings.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: JOE ROOT IS STUMPED! LOVELY BY ALEX CAREY!

children.content: Root was trying to get to his fifty in one blow and went barrelling down the deck, trying to heave Nathan Lyon over cow corner, but the ball dipped and spun through the gate and Alex Carey completed a superb stumping.
Lyon was coming around the wicket, so Carey's view of the ball would've been obscured for most of its journey.
Great play from Carey. Jonny Bairstow could never.
Missed opportunity for Joe Root, but the half-century was never the point of this innings.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: That's a stunning delivery from Pat Cummins! A perfect inswinging yorker. Well, he's not bowled perfectly so far this morning, but that was as close to a perfect delivery as you're likely to see - amazing ball from the Australian skipper. He goes for 13 off 16 balls.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: BOWLED HIM! POPE GOES!
